@startuml
skinparam rectangleStyle rounded
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam ArrowColor #555
skinparam ArrowThickness 1.2
skinparam PackageStyle rectangle
skinparam defaultFontName monospace

title WildWeb3 - High Level Architecture

actor User

rectangle "Streamlit Frontend\n(frontend container)" as FE
rectangle "FastAPI Backend\n(python-backend container)" as BE
cloud "Blockchain Network\n(RPC Provider)" as RPC

database "PostgreSQL\n(postgres_db container)" as PG
rectangle "pgAdmin\n(my_pgadmin container)" as PGADMIN

User --> FE : Interact via UI\nHTTP (8501)
FE --> BE : API Calls\nHTTP (8040)
BE --> RPC : JSON-RPC via Web3.py

BE ..> PG : future integration\n(DB schema exists)
PGADMIN --> PG : DB inspection

@enduml
